) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tLeaving the premise with the items would be out of the question since the club manager would know someone broke into his space immediately. If he could not take the things with him, there was no point to open the safe in the first place. Doug's decision was to forgo breaking into the safe and to get out. The only thing he did was just to take a picture of the safe to identify the type and model of the safe, as well as its security system. He could do the analysis later.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169500403971/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827501/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827501\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p824156/\">早上干这8件事，你的一天都会不一样</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767739/\">段子手的自白：我是如何从421进化到515的！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p839767/\">2017雅思考试时间表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p819221/\">BBC榜单：世界最伟大10家博物馆</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p844765/\">好的吧，现在连狗都出来虐狗了[微笑.jpg]</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p773848/\">学会说不 设定界限后你的生活发生这10件大事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p828475/\">外国人最喜欢看的竟然是这些书</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p844757/\">别人家的旅游照：在大自然面前渺小的我们</a></